'''貝西恩·伊特列查'''（'''{{lang-de|Besian Idrizaj}}'''，{{bd|1987年|10月12日|2010年|5月15日|catIdx=Idrizaj ,Besian}}），是一名前[[奧地利|奧地利]]足球員，司職[[足球前鋒|前鋒]]。他最後效力的是[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[史雲斯足球會|史雲斯]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.swanseacity.net/page/Latest/0,,10354~2053137,00.html |title=Agent reports sad death of Besian Idrizaj |publisher=Swansea City A.F.C. |date=2010-05-15 |accessdate=2010-05-16 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

2010年5月15日，年僅22歲的他被懷疑死於心臟病發<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Former-Liverpool-starlet-Besian-Idrizaj-dies-of-heart-attack-aged-just-22-article427331.html |title=Former Liverpool striker dies of heart-attack aged just 22 |publisher=The Daily Mirror |date=2010-05-15 |accessdate=2010-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100518044410/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Former-Liverpool-starlet-Besian-Idrizaj-dies-of-heart-attack-aged-just-22-article427331.html |archivedate=2010-05-18 }}</ref>。

== 球會 ==
;利物浦
伊特列查在阿德米拉林茨（Admira Linz）展開其足球生涯，其後加盟[[林茨足球會|林茨]]。2005年夏天，他在試訓後轉投[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]並簽訂兩年合約<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/4198046.stm |title=Liverpool bring in teenage pair |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2005-08-30 |accessdate=2010-05-23 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307022704/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/4198046.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他亦於2004/05球季成為奧地利最佳青年球員。當時他稱：「我一直是利物浦的球迷，能代表他們上陣簡直是夢想成真。如果你有機會去利物浦試訓，那麼你必須爭取。你不能忽視在衛冕歐聯冠軍的球會的試訓。我甚至願意游過海峽對岸只是為了試訓。」

2005/06球季，伊特列查飽受傷患困擾。然而，他在2006/07球季卻有望成為{{Link-en|加里·布萊特|Gary Ablett (English footballer)}}和{{Link-en|休·麥考利|Hughie McAuley}}的預備組的常規球員。2006年7月15日，他在季前友賽對[[域斯咸足球會|域斯咸]]的賽事中首次正選上陣，並且在上半場夥拍同樣是處子上陣的[[奇治·比拿美|奇治·比拿美]]進攻。

2007年7月7日，他在對域斯咸的友賽中於26分鐘內大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，三球皆由[[謝美伊·賓納|謝美伊·賓納]]助攻<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wrexham/6280934.stm |title=Idrizaj gives Reds win at Wrexham |publisher=BBC News |date=2007-07-07 |accessdate=2010-05-16 |archive-date=2007-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070819120332/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wrexham/6280934.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;盧頓
2007年3月16日，伊特列查被外借至[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[盧頓足球會|盧頓]]，直至2006/07球季結束<ref name="luton">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/drilldown/N155306070316-1215.htm|title=Idrizaj sent on loan to Luton|work=Liverpoolfc.tv|date=2006-03-16|accessdate=2007-03-16|archive-date=2007-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070319181512/http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/drilldown/N155306070316-1215.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月17日，他在對[[葉士域治足球會|葉士域治]]的賽事中首次於英格蘭聯賽正選上陣，但在49分鐘時被換下<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6437365.stm |title=Luton 0-2 Ipswich |work=Match report on BBC Sport |date=17 March 2007 |accessdate=17 March 2007 |archive-date=2007-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071002151637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6437365.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後，他繼續代表球會上陣了六次，並在對[[修安聯足球會|修安聯]]的賽事中取得入球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6578811.stm |title=Southend 1-3 Luton |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2007-04-28 |accessdate=2010-05-23 |archive-date=2007-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070913153732/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6578811.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;水晶宮
8月30日，伊特列查被外借至[[水晶宮足球會|水晶宮]]為期一年<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/crystal_palace/6970086.stm |title=Idrizaj poised for Palace move |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2007-08-30 |accessdate=2010-05- |archive-date=2013-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019133725/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/crystal_palace/6970086.stm |dead-url=no }}23</ref>。

9月1日，伊特列查在對[[查爾頓足球會|查爾頓]]的南倫敦打比進行至72分鐘時入替{{Link-en|克林頓·摩利臣|Clinton Morrison}}而首次上陣<ref name="idrizaj">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.cpfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/News/0,,10323~1101902,00.html|title=Palace Sign Reds Striker|work=cpfc.premiumtv.co.uk|date=2007-08-30|accessdate=2007-08-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415124112/http://www.cpfc.co.uk/page/News/0%2C%2C10323~1101902%2C00.html|archivedate=2012-04-15}}</ref>。然而，他未能在水晶宮取得正選位置。2008年1月，時任領隊[[尼爾·禾諾克|尼爾·禾諾克]]要求利物浦在一月轉會市場時將他收回。1月31日，他在水晶宮的借用期提早結束後，他自行同意在2007/08球季的剩餘時間外借至[[奧咸足球會|奧咸]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0500liverpoolfc/gronudmove/tm_headline=meeting-with-george-gillett-and-tom-hicks-over-stadium-not-rafa-benitez%26method=full%26objectid=20328568%26page=2%26siteid=50061-name_page.html|title=Meeting with George Gillett and Tom Hicks over stadium not Rafa Benitez|date=2008-01-09|accessdate=2008-01-09|archive-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516182405/http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0500liverpoolfc/gronudmove/tm_headline%3Dmeeting-with-george-gillett-and-tom-hicks-over-stadium-not-rafa-benitez%26method%3Dfull%26objectid%3D20328568%26page%3D2%26siteid%3D50061-name_page.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，在伊特列查的經理人阻撓下，他最終決定不加盟奧咸<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.oldhamathletic.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1230410,00.html|title=IDRIZAJ LOAN DEAL OFF|date=31 January 2008|accessdate=2008-01-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203204601/http://www.oldhamathletic.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsUpdate/0,,10337~1230410,00.html|archivedate=2008-02-03}}</ref>。

;重返奧地利
2008年1月31日，伊特列查被外借至奧地利球會[[因斯布魯克華卡迪路足球會|因斯布魯克]]，直至2007/08球季結束。他在對[[格拉茨足球會|格拉茨]]的賽事期間於球場上倒下<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/may/16/swansea-besian-idrizaj-paulo-sousa |title=Swansea City manager Paulo Sousa pays tribute to Besian Idrizaj |publisher=The Guardian |date=16 May 2010 |accessdate=16 May 2010 |archive-date=2010-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100519133806/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/may/16/swansea-besian-idrizaj-paulo-sousa |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，經過醫療檢查後，結果指暈倒是由於病毒而非心臟問題，從而讓他的足球生涯能夠繼續<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.thisissouthwales.co.uk/news/article-1909472-detail/article.html|title=Besian hopes to repay faith after fearing for pro career|publisher=South Wales Evening Post|date=13 March 2010|accessdate=16 May 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100519140012/http://www.thisissouthwales.co.uk/news/article-1909472-detail/article.html|archive-date=2010-05-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。其後，他被利物浦所放棄。

;艾倫堡
伊特列查代表{{Link-en|艾倫堡足球會|FC Eilenburg|艾倫堡}}上陣了五場賽事，並在代表球會上陣的第二場時獲得一面紅牌<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ww482.w3sserv.de/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=455&Itemid=68 |title=Keine Punkte auf der Müllerwiese |publisher=FC Eilenburg |date=2009-05-04 |language=de |accessdate=2010-05-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311191412/http://www.fceilenburg.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=455&Itemid=68 |archivedate=2012-03-11 }}</ref>。

;史雲斯
2009年8月18日，伊特列查前往[[史雲斯足球會|史雲斯]]試訓<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8206620.stm |title=Austrian forward in Swans trial |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2009-08-18 |accessdate=2010-05-23 |archive-date=2009-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090821132750/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8206620.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於8月24日正式加盟<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8216155.stm |title=Swansea recruit Austrian Idrizaj |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2009-08-24 |accessdate=2010-05-23 |archive-date=2009-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090827033834/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8216155.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。時任史雲斯領隊[[保羅·蘇沙|保羅·蘇沙]]讚揚他：「他不是前鋒，但他是一名攻擊球員，我知道了很多關於他和他這類型的球員，他們都能融入我們的球隊。」他在試訓期間的表現使史雲斯領隊留下深刻印象，他亦獲准在對[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]和[[高雲地利足球會|高雲地利]]的賽事中上陣。據稱，他在8月22日對高雲地利的賽事期間便獲球會提供合約，而他則在半場休息期間簽訂合約。他在該季代表史雲斯上陣三場，而球會則差點取得英冠附加賽資格和升班[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]的機會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.transfermarkt.de/de/news/30690/idrizaj-zu-swansea.html |title=Idrizaj zu Swansea |publisher=Transfermarkt |date=2009-08-23 |language=de |accessdate=2010-05-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091001224934/http://transfermarkt.de/de/news/30690/idrizaj-zu-swansea.html |archivedate=2009-10-01 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8216155.stm|title=Swansea recruit Austrian Idrizaj|date=2009-08-24|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2009-08-24|archive-date=2009-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090827033834/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8216155.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==逝世==
2010年5月15日，在英冠結束後僅兩週，只有22歲的伊特列查逝世。報告顯示，他在睡夢中死於心臟病發<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8684783.stm |title=Swansea player Besian Idrizaj dies at 22 |publisher=BBC News |date=15 May 2010 |accessdate=2010-05-15}}</ref>。另外，伊特列查亦曾在2008年11月於林茨試訓期間及2月代表因斯布魯克上陣的賽事中暈倒<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/may/15/besian-idrizaj-liverpool-swansea-austria |title=Swansea striker Besian Idrizaj dies of suspected heart attack aged 22 |publisher=guardian.co.uk |date=15 May 2010 |accessdate=2010-05-16 |archive-date=2010-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100518185024/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/may/15/besian-idrizaj-liverpool-swansea-austria |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.oe24.at/sport/fussball/Besian-Idrizaj-tot-Herzinfarkt-mit-22-Jahren-0709275.ece |title=Besian Idrizaj stirbt mit 22 Jahren |date=15 May 2010 |accessdate=2010-05-16 |archive-date=2010-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100518073420/http://www.oe24.at/sport/fussball/Besian-Idrizaj-tot-Herzinfarkt-mit-22-Jahren-0709275.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後，史雲斯宣佈將伊特列查所穿的40號球衣退役<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8690644.stm|title=Swansea City retire Besian Idrizaj's number 40 shirt|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2010-05-18|accessdate=2010-05-23|archive-date=2010-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100521073801/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8690644.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

